6.Delete the first two records of INVOICE_ITEM table.

mysql> select * from Invoice_item;
+--------+------+---------+
| inv_id | pid  | quality |
+--------+------+---------+
|    104 |    5 |       6 |
|    105 |    4 |       2 |
|    103 |    3 |       5 |
+--------+------+---------+
3 rows in set (0.00 sec)

mysql> delete from Invoice_item LIMIT 2;
Query OK, 2 rows affected (0.00 sec)

mysql> select * from Invoice_item;
+--------+------+---------+
| inv_id | pid  | quality |
+--------+------+---------+
|    103 |    3 |       5 |
+--------+------+---------+
1 row in set (0.00 sec)




